{"tid":2023734,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[又加] PC起薪就黎26k  公務員料今年加薪1.68%至1.98%","createTime":"2020-05-19T07:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T23:08:43.000Z","uid":116083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fab8e063526b3da2f81a70ce214d0ac4304aefc9","tid":2023734,"uid":116083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:38:11.000Z","msg":"影響近18萬公務員的薪酬趨勢調查出爐，在武漢肺炎疫情下，高層公務員今年料獲加薪1.68%，中、低層則加1.98%，幅度為近10年新低。<br />\n<br />\n薪酬趨勢調查委員會發表報告，依據過去1年逾百間公司的僱員薪酬和花紅變動，得出今年私營機構高、中及低層僱員的加薪幅度為2.72%、3.01%及2.31%，政府計算公務員加薪指標時，會按機制先扣減遞增薪額，雖今年遞增薪額再創回歸後新高，高、中及低層公務員分別為1.24%、1.28%及2.3%，但由於政府去年起已為遞增薪額設封頂機制，因此今年只須分別扣減1.04%、1.03%及1.16%，經扣減後，薪酬趨勢淨指標為高層1.68%、中層1.98%及低層1.15%。<br />\n<br />\n政府通常會依據淨指標調整公務員薪酬，按照慣例，低層加幅與中層看齊，即今年中、低層公務員料加薪1.98%，高層則加薪1.68%，委員會下周二（26日）開會審核報告，若獲職方代表確認，再交由行政會議拍板及立法會審批，加薪可追溯至今年4月1日起生效。首長級官員一般會跟隨高級公務員加薪幅度調薪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200519&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60956162\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200519%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60956162&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=804c077f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200519%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60956162&h=55ab820f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200519&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60956162</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-constable/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.govtjobsdb.com%2Fpolice-constable%2F&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=a9d585a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.govtjobsdb.com/police-constable/</a><br />\nPolice Constable 警員<br />\n(PPS 3 &ndash; 15)<br />\n$25,380 &ndash; $36,290<br />\n<br />\n25380 +1.98% -&gt; 25880 xx[/red][/b]("},{"pid":"bf2df6608d22bd2aa31c77509bc0e9442b809654","tid":2023734,"uid":74171,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:51:28.000Z","msg":"邊撚度值26k"},{"pid":"442cc48a85773962371136d99d09002e2c8f7b25","tid":2023734,"uid":190604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"萬六都俾多佢地<br />\n字都唔撚識多隻"},{"pid":"f64fe604cca019deb1dfa765820572fa8d94e1d8","tid":2023734,"uid":72991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"442cc48a85773962371136d99d09002e2c8f7b25","tid":2023734,"uid":190604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T07:52:22.000Z","msg":"萬六都俾多佢地<br />\n字都唔撚識多隻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T11:27:12.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"30df699160eb2b011376f93adb4fea794d795106","tid":2023734,"uid":116396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T23:08:43.000Z","msg":"16k就合理"}]}